'''''Vode An''''', meaning "'''Brothers All'''," was a [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] war chant sung in [[Mando'a/Legends|''Mando'a'']]. Notably, before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]] personally trained the first batch of Alpha-class [[Advanced Recon Commando/Legends|ARC]] [[Trooper/Legends|troopers]] for the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]]. Fett instilled these [[Clone trooper/Legends|clones]] with Mandalorian values, including having each clone memorize the ''Vode An''. Other clones, including [[Clone commando/Legends|Clone Commandos]], were taught the ''Vode An'' by their various Mandalorian trainers. This group of Mandalorians were brought to Kamino on Jango's request to train many of the more advanced clones; they were known as the [[Cuy'val Dar]]. The song referred to them as the "Wrath of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]," which had a dual meaning, since they were being used by the Republic, and Coruscant was the original [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the Mandalorians. The chant was famously sung by the clone troopers with the accompaniment of [[Drum/Legends|drums]] and [[Horn/Legends|horns]]. A variant was created for the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] and sung by Commandos [[Fi Skirata|Fi]] and [[Niner Skirata]].

==Lyrics==

<center>
{| {{Prettytable}}
! [[Mando'a/Legends|''Mando'a'']]||[[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]]
|-
|colspan="1"|''Kote!<br />Kandosii sa ka'rta, Vode an.<br />Coruscanta a'den mhi, Vode an.<br />Bal kote, darasuum kote,<br />Jorso'ran kando a tome.<br />Sa kyr'am nau tracyn kad, Vode an.<br /><br />Kandosii sa ka'rta, Vode an.<br />Coruscanta a'den mhi, Vode an.<br />Bal...<br />Motir ca'tra nau tracinya.<br />Gra'tua cuun hett su dralshy'a.<br />Aruetyc runi solus cet o'r.<br />Motir ca'tra nau tracinya.<br />Gra'tua cuun hett su dralshy'a.<br />Aruetyc runi trattok'o.<br />Sa kyr'am nau tracyn kad, Vode an!''||colspan="1"|Glory!<br />One indomitable heart, Brothers all.<br />We, the wrath of Coruscant, Brothers all.<br />And glory, eternal glory,<br />We shall bear its weight together.<br />Forged like the saber in the fires of death, Brothers all.<br /><br />One indomitable heart, Brothers all.<br />We, the wrath of Coruscant, Brothers all.<br />And...<br />Those who stand before us light the night sky in flame.<br />Our vengeance burns brighter still.<br />Every last traitorous soul shall kneel.<br />Those who stand before us light the night sky in flame.<br />Our vengeance burns brighter still.<br />Every last traitorous soul shall fall.<br />Forged like the saber in the fires of death, Brothers all!<br />
|}
</center>

