==Behind the scenes==
''Vode An'' is heard throughout several parts of the 2005 video game ''[[Star Wars: Republic Commando]]'', including the main menu and several battle sequences. In 2016 the song, along with several other pieces of music from ''Republic Commando'', was reused for the Mandalorian-centric "Chapter XIV: Mandalore's Revenge" of ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire]]''.

An instrumentation of part of ''Vode An''{{'s}} chorus briefly plays as clone commando [[Gregor]] lay dying in the finale of the [[canon]] animated television series ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]'', "[[Family Reunion – and Farewell]]," which first aired in [[2018]].<ref name="Family Reunion">{{Rebels|Family Reunion &ndash; and Farewell}}</ref>

